codeGet:
select guruobj_userid as USER_ID from bansecr.GURUOBJ where guruobj_OBJECT in('GPBADMN','GPBADMNA')  and GURUOBJ_USERID not like 'BAN_%'
union
select GURUCLS_userid as USER_ID from bansecr.gurucls
where gurucls_class_code in (select GURUOBJ_USERID from bansecr.GURUOBJ where guruobj_OBJECT in('GPBADMN','GPBADMNA')  and GURUOBJ_USERID like 'BAN_%')
